{"id":384580,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/03/【麻辣总局】真理部官员聊风水/","date":"2015-03-07T07:53:31Z","modified":"2015-03-07T07:53:31Z","title":"【麻辣总局】真理部官员聊风水","content":"<p>真理部一帮官员无事闲聊风水：“我五行缺金，所以叫赵鑫。”“我缺木，叫钱森。”“ 我缺水，叫孙淼。”“ 我缺火，叫李焱。”“ 我缺土，叫周垚。”一人推门进来边作揖边说：“给各位领导请安！我叫王晶。已经和黄秋生、何韵诗断交啦！ ” </p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/03/B0HezjZCYAA-r4j.jpg\" alt=\"B0HezjZCYAA-r4j\" width=\"548\" height=\"367\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-384581\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/03/B0HezjZCYAA-r4j.jpg 548w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/03/B0HezjZCYAA-r4j-300x201.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 548px) 100vw, 548px\" /></p>\n","author":1001,"categories":[18270,18269,13789],"tags":[26002]}